Rute:

Toate rutele sunt similare; se suporta implicit CRUD (create, retrieve, update, delete). Call-urile sunt ca mai jos:

url-uri implementate:

/users
/teams
/projects
/tasks
/meetings
/messages
/documents - pentru atasamente la proiecte


Exemplu: Teams
API CALLS

Get list of all teams
	http://server/teams

Get details for a team id:
	http://server/teams/{id}


GET:
	/teams - get list of all teams
	/teams/1 - get details for team with id 1
	/teams/for/4 - get team details for manager with id 4

POST:
	/teams - add a new team


** pentru update si delete, se foloseste HTTP POST, si se trimite un camp in plus, _method = PUT sau DELETE

PUT:
	/teams/1 - update team with id 1

DELETE:
	/teams/1 - delete team with id 1